OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775308265
OL,3,CConvicted sex offender who groomed
OL,4,CAmerican teenager admits 67 other
OL,5,Ccrimes
OL,7,FA convicted sex offender who groomed
OL,8,Fan American teenager has been jailed
OL,9,Ffor life after pleading guilty to 67
OL,10,Fother crimes against "highly
OL,11,Fvulnerable young girls" between the
OL,12,Fages of one and 16.
OL,14,FTrevor Fernandes, 41, from Swindon,
OL,15,Fwas jailed for 14 years in 2022 after
OL,16,Fbeing convicted of grooming and
OL,17,Fblackmailing a 13-year old girl in
OL,18,FAmerica into abusing herself and
OL,19,Fanother child.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
