OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775308265
OL,3,CConvicted sex offender who groomed
OL,4,CAmerican teenager admits 67 other
OL,5,Ccrimes
OL,7,FHe was arrested by National Crime
OL,8,FAgency officers in 2020, after she
OL,9,Freported the abuse to police in
OL,10,FGarland, Texas.
OL,12,FShe explained that she had been in
OL,13,Fcommunication with someone called
OL,14,F'Trevor' online for months, who had
OL,15,Fforced her to send him sexualised
OL,16,Fimages of herself.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775308265
OL,3,CConvicted sex offender who groomed
OL,4,CAmerican teenager admits 67 other
OL,5,Ccrimes
OL,7,FOver time, Fernandes' requests became
OL,8,Fmore extreme, and he threatened to
OL,9,Fsend images and footage she'd already
OL,10,Fsent to her friends and family if she
OL,11,Frefused to do as he asked.
OL,13,FWhile he was in jail, officers
OL,14,Fcontinued to monitor Fernandes' phone,
OL,15,Funcovering more offences against
OL,16,Fvictims across England, America,
OL,17,FCanada, Ireland and Norway.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775308265
OL,3,CConvicted sex offender who groomed
OL,4,CAmerican teenager admits 67 other
OL,5,Ccrimes
OL,7,FIn September 2025, he was charged with
OL,8,Fan additional 67 offences, including
OL,9,Fblackmail, causing or inciting sexual
OL,10,Factivity with a child, malicious
OL,11,Fcommunication, causing a child to
OL,12,Fwatch a sexual act and making and
OL,13,Fdistributing indecent images of
OL,14,Fchildren.
OL,16,FOn Thursday, 2 April 2026, Fernandes
OL,17,Fwas jailed for life, with a minimum of
OL,18,F13 years and eight months to serve.
OL,20,F"Highly vulnerable young girls"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775308265
OL,3,CConvicted sex offender who groomed
OL,4,CAmerican teenager admits 67 other
OL,5,Ccrimes
OL,7,FHanding down the sentence, HHJ Taylor
OL,8,FKC described the crimes as "some of
OL,9,Fthe worst offending of this type to
OL,10,Fcome before the court" against "highly
OL,11,Fvulnerable young girls."
OL,13,FDanielle Pownall, Senior Investigating
OL,14,FOfficer at the National Crime Agency,
OL,15,Fsaid: "Fernandes is a prolific and
OL,16,Fdangerous child sex offender and knew
OL,17,Fat the time of his original conviction
OL,18,Fthat there were more children he had
OL,19,Fabused.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775308265
OL,3,CConvicted sex offender who groomed
OL,4,CAmerican teenager admits 67 other
OL,5,Ccrimes
OL,7,F"He used threats and blackmail to
OL,8,Fcoerce young children to commit
OL,9,Fhorrendous acts, and the sentence
OL,10,Fgiven today highlights the severity of
OL,11,Fthat offending.
OL,13,F"The young girl who reported the abuse
OL,14,Fto the authorities in the US showed
OL,15,Fincredible bravery in coming forward
OL,16,Fand telling police what had happened
OL,17,Fto her. Without her courage, Fernandes
OL,18,Fwould potentially still be sexually
OL,19,Fabusing children, and I would like to
OL,20,Fthank her again for taking that step
OL,21,Fand facing her fears.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775308265
OL,3,CConvicted sex offender who groomed
OL,4,CAmerican teenager admits 67 other
OL,5,Ccrimes
OL,7,F"Officers in the UK, specifically the
OL,8,Flead officer and investigation team,
OL,9,Ftogether with officers in the US and
OL,10,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service, have
OL,11,Fworked tirelessly to ensure Fernandes
OL,12,Fis held accountable for his actions.
OL,14,F"Their tenacity and resilience during
OL,15,Fthis investigation has identified
OL,16,Fhundreds of victims, located all
OL,17,Faround the world, who have been
OL,18,Fsubject to safeguarding activity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775308265
OL,3,CConvicted sex offender who groomed
OL,4,CAmerican teenager admits 67 other
OL,5,Ccrimes
OL,7,FJeanette Smith, specialist prosecutor
OL,8,Fin the CPS's Organised Child Sexual
OL,9,FAbuse Unit, added: "Trevor Fernandes's
OL,10,Frepulsive actions saw him use social
OL,11,Fmedia to control, exploit and damage
OL,12,Fyoung girls ` aged between 1 and 16 `
OL,13,Fin England, America, Canada, Ireland
OL,14,Fand Norway.
OL,26,@qD@TOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
