PN,43609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775308265
OL,3,CConvicted sex offender who groomed
OL,4,CAmerican teenager admits 67 other
OL,5,Ccrimes
OL,7,F"This case involved working with a
OL,8,Fnumber of international partners to
OL,9,Fdemonstrate the scale of Fernandes's
OL,10,Foffences and to ensure he faces
OL,11,Fjustice for everything he has
OL,12,Fsubjected his victims to, and enable
OL,13,Fthe court to pass a sentence which
OL,14,Fprotects other young girls now and in
OL,15,Fthe future.
OL,17,F"If you are in an abusive online
OL,18,Fsituation, talk to someone ` like some
OL,19,Fof the victims did in this case ` so
OL,20,Fyou can get help and perpetrators can
OL,21,Fbe brought to justice."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU}D@WO]
